  "detailed_description": "With up to four players, choose to battle each other in free for all with a variety of weapons ranging from a simple pistol to a sumo suit! Not a fan of beating your friends? Battle alongside or alone against waves of different zombies constantly getting stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406350/extras/e16bb61e3d925e5aff8cf2aa2013e8b0.avif?t=1600886548\" width=540 height=118 /></span><br>- Single Player / Local Multiplayer up to 4 players<br>- 2+ players recommended<br>- Use of steam remote play recommended<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406350/extras/dade21c6d8e80e5039eee24ae2be09f2.avif?t=1600886548\" width=540 height=118 /></span><br>- 2+ players required<br>- Modifiers to adjust stats such as health and weapon drop rates<br>- Custom Win Messages<br>- 21 Maps<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406350/extras/448a4ffc64e328fc58a095fb322bd0e2.avif?t=1600886548\" width=540 height=118 /></span><br>- 1-4 players<br>- 3 different maps<br>- Progressively stronger zombies as well as bosses and types of zombies<br>- Perks and weapon cannon",
